animeDescription: Lala-chan is a slightly selfish squirrel girl. On her birthday the gifts given to her by her friends go awry. The group gets teleported into a new world (Earth) where they try to retrieve the elemental magic crystal balls that bring balance in their world.
animeRelated: ['Side story: Lalala Lala-chan Mini', 'Sequel: Lalala Lala-chan: Patapata Daisensou']
